    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been fastidiously maintained by a single owner. The exterior finish is flawless, retaining its original deep luster without a single stone chip, scratch, or swirl mark. Inside, the cabin remains in as-new condition; the premium leather seats show no wear, the dashboard is pristine, and all electronics function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history and a drive that feels exactly as it did when it first left the dealership. This is a rare opportunity to own a perfectly preserved example of this model.",
