    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road? I\u2019m parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-maintained, super clean, and runs like a dream. It\u2019s got a few miles of memories on it, but it\u2019s totally ready to make plenty more with you. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
