      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car featuring the iconic S54B32 atmospheric inline-six, delivering linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The dual-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled to ensure precise valve timing, and the rod bearings\u2014a critical preventative maintenance item\u2014have been replaced. Power is routed through a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis has been proactively reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points to mitigate common floor-pan fatigue. The suspension features refreshed bushings and upgraded dampers, maintaining strict compliance during high-lateral-G cornering. While the body exhibits minor cosmetic patina from road use, the drivetrain and structural vitals are optimized for peak performance.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used sedan. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. Test drives welcome.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
