    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that offers a superb blend of performance and comfort. The exterior paint retains a brilliant gloss, showing only minor, expected road wear that does not detract from its impressive curb appeal. Step inside to a pristine, non-smoking cabin where the leather upholstery remains supple and the dashboard remains free of cracks or fading. Every feature, from the responsive infotainment screen to the heated seats and dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs smoothly, benefiting from a documented history of on-time oil changes and a recent multi-point inspection. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This car has been driven with care and is ready for its next owner to enjoy many more miles of reliable service.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
