    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 and a 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission. This unit delivers a linear torque curve and crisp throttle response via eight individual throttle bodies. Preventative maintenance is up to date, including reinforced rod bearings and replaced throttle actuators. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity with a functioning M Variable Differential Lock and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing excellent lateral grip. While the aesthetics show minor signs of spirited road use, the drivetrain remains robust with no subframe fatigue or VANOS issues. A purist\u2019s spec optimized for performance.",
